      "source": [
        "# 🏠 House Price Prediction — V12 (XGB + LGB + CatBoost Ensemble + Stacking)\n",
        "\n",
        "**Consolidated upgrades (V12)**:\n",
        "- **Outlier removal**: price/m2 IQR outliers and IsolationForest.\n",
        "- **Features**: Consolidated geographic distances, spatial density, district benchmarks, and 30 NLP features (derived from combined title + description search).\n",
        "- **Tuning**: Optuna tuning for XGBoost, LightGBM, and CatBoost.\n",
        "- **Ensemble**: Ridge stacking regressor on 5-fold out-of-fold predictions, blended with optimal weights grid search.\n",
        "- **Metadata & Save**: Models saved directly to the Lakehouse directory as `master_*_v12.joblib` and `model_meta_v12.json` (also mapped to `final`/`master` names)."
      ]
